  <brief_title>Ketamine Prevent POCD</brief_title>
  <acronym>KPPOCD</acronym>
  <official_title>Low Dose Ketamine Prevent the Postoperative Cognitive Dysfunction in Aged Patients Underwent Orthopaedic Surgery，a Randomized Control Double Blinded Multicenter Clinical Trail</official_title>
